WorldStage Newsonline– United Capital Plc, a leading financial services Group in Africa with focus on leveraging technology to empower businesses, individuals and governments has confirmed a Director/Insider dealing on 1,000,000 shares which worth N3.2 million at N3.0320 per share. In a note to the Nigerian Stock Exchange (NSE) by Leo Okafor, Company Secretary confirmed that  Emanuel Nnorom/Vine Foods Limited, a related company was the inside buyer in a transaction which took place on August 19, 2020.